20
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:36,580
=My Destined Consort=

21
00:01:36,660 --> 00:01:39,660
=Episode 10=

22
00:01:47,730 --> 00:01:49,020
What are you waiting for?

23
00:01:49,020 --> 00:01:50,090
Hurry up and think of a way

24
00:01:50,090 --> 00:01:51,580
to stop the Prefect's pain!

25
00:01:52,140 --> 00:01:53,090
My Lady,

26
00:01:53,170 --> 00:01:55,530
I've administered acupuncture
and medicine to the Prefect,

27
00:01:55,780 --> 00:01:57,220
but the old illness is stubborn.

28
00:01:57,450 --> 00:01:58,600
The Prefect is now suffering

29
00:01:58,890 --> 00:02:00,300
from a surge of anger

30
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:01,340
that worsens his condition.

31
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:02,530
I currently

32
00:02:02,700 --> 00:02:04,220
can't find any way to relieve it.

33
00:02:04,940 --> 00:02:05,890
You're useless.

34
00:02:06,220 --> 00:02:07,430
- Leave.
- Yes.

35
00:02:11,210 --> 00:02:12,050
Xiulan,

36
00:02:12,820 --> 00:02:14,540
you should go rest.

37
00:02:14,890 --> 00:02:16,650
I'll stay and serve the Prefect.

38
00:02:17,540 --> 00:02:18,820
No need to trouble you.

39
00:02:18,990 --> 00:02:20,770
Every time the Prefect's headache
flares up,

40
00:02:20,770 --> 00:02:22,140
I've been the one to attend to him.

41
00:02:22,650 --> 00:02:23,490
I know

42
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:24,730
the pressure of the massage.

43
00:02:29,300 --> 00:02:30,140
Qinian,

44
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:32,170
you haven't had your dinner yet.

45
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:33,690
Would you like to have dinner now?

46
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:39,030
My Lord, Consort Jiangli
seeks an audience.

47
00:02:39,610 --> 00:02:40,610
What does she want?

48
00:02:41,490 --> 00:02:42,730
The Prefect is unwell.

49
00:02:42,730 --> 00:02:43,650
Tell her

50
00:02:43,650 --> 00:02:44,490
to come another day.

51
00:02:44,700 --> 00:02:45,080
My Lady,

52
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:47,480
Consort Jiangli heard
the Prefect's headache had flared up,

53
00:02:47,540 --> 00:02:48,580
so she came to treat him.

54
00:02:49,210 --> 00:02:50,450
She's not a physician.

55
00:02:50,450 --> 00:02:52,320
She doesn't know anything.
Tell her to leave.

56
00:02:53,020 --> 00:02:53,860
Wait.

57
00:02:54,330 --> 00:02:55,170
Xiulan,

58
00:02:55,580 --> 00:02:57,140
I heard that she treated

59
00:02:57,140 --> 00:02:58,380
Qingqing's face injury.

60
00:02:59,210 --> 00:03:00,170
Why not let her try?

61
00:03:00,730 --> 00:03:01,830
What do you think, Qinian?

62
00:03:01,930 --> 00:03:03,100
Let her in.

63
00:03:03,450 --> 00:03:04,290
Yes.

64
00:03:14,610 --> 00:03:15,580
Greetings, My Lord,

65
00:03:15,580 --> 00:03:17,050
Lady Wang, Lady Shu.

66
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:19,630
I heard that the Prefect's headache
flared up,

67
00:03:19,650 --> 00:03:20,650
so I came to treat him.

68
00:03:21,580 --> 00:03:23,140
The private physicians couldn't cure it.

69
00:03:23,450 --> 00:03:24,730
Stop fooling around.

70
00:03:24,730 --> 00:03:25,860
Go back now.

71
00:03:26,650 --> 00:03:29,730
Xiulan, Jiangli has good intentions.

72
00:03:30,170 --> 00:03:31,420
Let her give it a try.

73
00:03:31,930 --> 00:03:33,890
Don't refuse her kindness.

74
00:03:34,540 --> 00:03:37,140
Sometimes, experience doesn't matter.

75
00:03:37,820 --> 00:03:39,380
Maybe she can cure the Prefect

76
00:03:39,380 --> 00:03:40,650
by accident.

77
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:42,610
Jinyi, you're wrong.

78
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:44,330
The Prefect's health

79
00:03:44,730 --> 00:03:46,260
cannot be handled recklessly.

80
00:03:46,580 --> 00:03:47,700
Enough.

81
00:03:48,540 --> 00:03:49,540
Since she's here,

82
00:03:49,820 --> 00:03:52,100
it's okay to let her feel the pulse.

83
00:03:52,610 --> 00:03:53,450
Yes.

84
00:04:11,450 --> 00:04:12,580
My Lord, your headache

85
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:14,700
is caused by blocked qi and blood flow.

86
00:04:15,490 --> 00:04:17,770
I need to use a triangular needle

87
00:04:17,770 --> 00:04:18,970
to bleed you.

88
00:04:20,770 --> 00:04:21,610
How dare you!

89
00:04:24,290 --> 00:04:25,770
You're being reckless.

90
00:04:26,500 --> 00:04:27,340
Bleeding?

91
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:30,060
If the Prefect's health worsens,

92
00:04:30,500 --> 00:04:31,940
can you take responsibility for it?

93
00:04:32,290 --> 00:04:33,130
Xiulan,

94
00:04:33,450 --> 00:04:35,410
if the Prefect misses treatment

95
00:04:35,410 --> 00:04:37,140
because you stopped it

96
00:04:37,700 --> 00:04:39,410
and continues to suffer,

97
00:04:39,740 --> 00:04:41,140
how will you live with yourself?

98
00:04:42,620 --> 00:04:43,460
But

99
00:04:43,820 --> 00:04:45,260
Father is sweating profusely.

100
00:04:45,650 --> 00:04:46,530
His collar is soaked.

101
00:04:47,060 --> 00:04:48,280
He must be in unbearable pain.

102
00:04:48,740 --> 00:04:49,890
If we don't treat it,

103
00:04:49,890 --> 00:04:51,090
it will harm him deeply.

104
00:04:51,700 --> 00:04:53,260
Lady Shu, please trust me

105
00:04:53,410 --> 00:04:54,450
and let me use the needle.

106
00:04:55,260 --> 00:04:56,180
Stop it.

107
00:04:56,180 --> 00:04:57,180
How can you fool around

108
00:04:57,180 --> 00:04:58,500
in the Prefect's Mansion?

109
00:04:58,740 --> 00:05:00,530
Don't make things worse with Jingming.

110
00:05:01,290 --> 00:05:02,390
Lady Shu, please calm down.

111
00:05:02,850 --> 00:05:04,290
Sorry for not thinking it through.

112
00:05:06,580 --> 00:05:07,420
But

113
00:05:07,770 --> 00:05:09,060
I have something

114
00:05:09,410 --> 00:05:10,770
that can relieve the Prefect's pain

115
00:05:11,580 --> 00:05:12,580
without being consumed.

116
00:05:12,580 --> 00:05:14,970
It can relieve the pain
and stop sweating.

117
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:17,750
Is it so miraculous?

118
00:05:18,090 --> 00:05:19,380
Hurry and show it to us.

119
00:05:20,970 --> 00:05:21,940
Shen Jiangli,

120
00:05:22,450 --> 00:05:24,020
you better be careful

121
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:25,210
when speaking here.

122
00:05:26,410 --> 00:05:27,250
Yes.

123
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:55,290
Your ink is quite special.

124
00:05:56,180 --> 00:05:58,740
It has a unique fragrance.

125
00:06:00,410 --> 00:06:01,820
After I smelled it,

126
00:06:02,210 --> 00:06:04,770
my headache eased significantly.

127
00:06:06,090 --> 00:06:06,930
I selected herbs

128
00:06:06,940 --> 00:06:09,210
that can calm the mind
and soothe the heart.

129
00:06:09,530 --> 00:06:11,450
I combined them with this inkstone

130
00:06:11,450 --> 00:06:12,650
and made this fragrance.

131
00:06:13,050 --> 00:06:13,890
It also helps

132
00:06:13,890 --> 00:06:15,190
focus the mind, calm the spirit,

133
00:06:15,260 --> 00:06:16,450
and stop sweating.

134
00:06:21,260 --> 00:06:22,100
Not bad.

135
00:06:24,380 --> 00:06:26,210
I've sweated much less now.

136
00:06:27,850 --> 00:06:28,690
Good.

137
00:06:30,820 --> 00:06:31,770
Amitabha.

138
00:06:32,290 --> 00:06:33,180
Amitabha.

139
00:06:34,380 --> 00:06:35,580
In the end, it was I

140
00:06:35,580 --> 00:06:37,450
who insisted on letting Jiangli try.

141
00:06:37,820 --> 00:06:39,140
I originally thought

142
00:06:39,650 --> 00:06:40,620
that if it didn't work,

143
00:06:40,970 --> 00:06:42,410
I'd take the punishment for her.

144
00:06:43,020 --> 00:06:43,940
Fortunately,

145
00:06:43,940 --> 00:06:46,180
Jiangli didn't let me down.

146
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:48,580
It won't come to that.

147
00:06:48,820 --> 00:06:51,410
After all, Jiangli
is my daughter-in-law.

148
00:06:51,550 --> 00:06:52,740
If anyone should be punished,

149
00:06:52,740 --> 00:06:54,770
it should be me.

150
00:06:55,260 --> 00:06:56,530
No need to trouble you.

151
00:06:57,110 --> 00:06:58,850
You can't discipline
your daughter-in-law.

152
00:06:58,850 --> 00:07:00,050
Stop trying to take mine.

153
00:07:01,650 --> 00:07:02,500
But

154
00:07:02,500 --> 00:07:04,740
this fragrance can only
temporarily ease the pain.

155
00:07:05,380 --> 00:07:06,450
To cure it completely,

156
00:07:06,770 --> 00:07:08,060
acupuncture is still needed.

157
00:07:08,580 --> 00:07:09,530
My Lord, please allow me

158
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:11,180
to perform acupuncture on you.

159
00:07:11,890 --> 00:07:12,730
Sure.

160
00:07:13,970 --> 00:07:14,820
Can the acupuncture

161
00:07:15,820 --> 00:07:16,660
cure it?

162
00:07:18,060 --> 00:07:18,900
Lady Shu,

163
00:07:19,740 --> 00:07:21,090
I once studied medicine

164
00:07:21,450 --> 00:07:23,380
at the ancestral tomb.

165
00:07:23,970 --> 00:07:26,060
One acupuncture session can only

166
00:07:26,060 --> 00:07:27,430
temporarily alleviate the headache.

167
00:07:27,700 --> 00:07:28,850
To cure it completely,

168
00:07:29,140 --> 00:07:30,500
it'll take at least six months.

169
00:08:09,210 --> 00:08:11,140
My mind feels much clearer now.

170
00:08:14,380 --> 00:08:15,220
Come on.

171
00:08:15,620 --> 00:08:16,530
Help me up.

172
00:08:17,580 --> 00:08:18,420
Help me up.

173
00:08:21,410 --> 00:08:22,250
Slowly.

174
00:08:26,890 --> 00:08:27,820
Jiangli has always

175
00:08:27,820 --> 00:08:29,970
cared about the Prefect's illness.

176
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:32,050
She's fulfilled her duty.

177
00:08:32,740 --> 00:08:35,650
This is what a daughter-in-law
should do.

178
00:08:38,050 --> 00:08:39,050
You are

179
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:41,690
both filial and capable.

180
00:08:41,930 --> 00:08:42,870
You should be rewarded.

181
00:08:43,980 --> 00:08:44,820
Thank you, My Lord.

182
00:08:45,140 --> 00:08:46,410
This is what I should do.

183
00:08:46,890 --> 00:08:49,460
I'll try my best to cure you.

184
00:08:50,410 --> 00:08:52,260
If you want to reward me,

185
00:08:53,140 --> 00:08:54,500
I have a request.

186
00:08:56,620 --> 00:08:57,690
What do you want?

187
00:08:58,930 --> 00:09:00,380
I want a medicine

188
00:09:01,140 --> 00:09:02,100
called the Lei Pill.

189
00:09:04,100 --> 00:09:06,050
Do you know
how precious the Lei Pill is?

190
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:07,410
I know.

191
00:09:08,260 --> 00:09:09,740
How dare you ask for them then?

192
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:12,410
Only someone
who once stabilized the nation

193
00:09:12,410 --> 00:09:13,890
can ask for it.

194
00:09:14,890 --> 00:09:15,770
Jiangli,

195
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,500
don't think
that just because you treated

196
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:19,260
the Prefect's headache,

197
00:09:19,260 --> 00:09:20,860
you can demand rewards

198
00:09:20,860 --> 00:09:22,100
and elevate yourself.

199
00:09:22,810 --> 00:09:25,050
My Lord, Jiangli

200
00:09:26,460 --> 00:09:27,890
has a loose tongue.

201
00:09:28,530 --> 00:09:30,140
Given that she treated your illness

202
00:09:30,140 --> 00:09:31,980
with care,

203
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:33,690
please don't blame her.

204
00:09:36,100 --> 00:09:37,050
Jiangli,

205
00:09:37,530 --> 00:09:40,290
I'll reward you with some jewelry,

206
00:09:40,460 --> 00:09:41,690
which will be more useful.

207
00:09:42,530 --> 00:09:44,290
I don't want jewelry.

208
00:09:44,290 --> 00:09:45,650
- I...
- Don't be rude.

209
00:09:47,340 --> 00:09:49,170
Treating the Prefect is your duty.

210
00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:50,670
You should thank the Prefect.

211
00:09:53,340 --> 00:09:54,180
Come on.

212
00:09:55,170 --> 00:09:57,620
Reward Consort Jiangli
with ten bolts of silk

213
00:09:58,020 --> 00:09:59,410
and two boxes of gold and jewels.

214
00:10:02,050 --> 00:10:02,980
Thank you, My Lord.

215
00:10:17,410 --> 00:10:18,470
I'll polish it a bit more.

216
00:11:08,810 --> 00:11:09,650
How is it?

217
00:11:10,940 --> 00:11:12,840
The Prefect didn't reward me
with the Lei Pill.

218
00:11:13,650 --> 00:11:14,490
It's okay.

219
00:11:15,260 --> 00:11:16,810
I believe that in a little more time,

220
00:11:17,050 --> 00:11:18,840
the Zhuge crossbow
will definitely succeed.

221
00:11:20,260 --> 00:11:22,410
So, how's it going
with the Zhuge crossbow?

222
00:11:25,500 --> 00:11:26,500
Logically speaking,

223
00:11:26,740 --> 00:11:28,460
the blueprints should be right.

224
00:11:29,050 --> 00:11:30,530
The craftsmen have made the appearance

225
00:11:30,770 --> 00:11:32,610
of the crossbow
according to the blueprints,

226
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:34,170
but something went wrong

227
00:11:34,170 --> 00:11:35,010
at some point.

228
00:11:35,740 --> 00:11:36,580
But don't worry.

229
00:11:37,050 --> 00:11:38,650
The craftsmen have been testing it

230
00:11:38,810 --> 00:11:39,770
day and night.

231
00:11:40,140 --> 00:11:40,980
My Lady,

232
00:11:41,690 --> 00:11:42,650
to make the crossbow,

233
00:11:42,650 --> 00:11:44,020
Master Jingming stayed up all night

234
00:11:44,020 --> 00:11:44,930
without a single bite.

235
00:11:44,930 --> 00:11:45,890
Please talk to him.

236
00:11:45,890 --> 00:11:46,730
You talk too much.

237
00:11:50,220 --> 00:11:51,060
From today on,

238
00:11:51,570 --> 00:11:52,650
I'll accompany you.

239
00:12:28,770 --> 00:12:29,650
Useless!

240
00:12:30,650 --> 00:12:32,410
Useless! Useless!

241
00:12:32,590 --> 00:12:33,760
A bunch of useless fools!

242
00:12:33,890 --> 00:12:34,960
How many days has it been?

243
00:12:35,020 --> 00:12:37,510
You can't even produce
a weapon blueprint.

244
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:38,940
Please calm down.

245
00:12:39,460 --> 00:12:40,410
The scout reports

246
00:12:40,410 --> 00:12:41,930
that the envoys have changed their plan

247
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:44,230
and are likely to arrive
ten days earlier.

248
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,650
Even if we finish the blueprint now,

249
00:12:45,650 --> 00:12:46,890
we won't have time to make it.

250
00:12:49,980 --> 00:12:50,820
Fine.

251
00:12:51,930 --> 00:12:53,340
Since I can't make it,

252
00:12:54,050 --> 00:12:55,740
I won't let anyone else produce it.

253
00:12:57,410 --> 00:12:59,410
Keep a close watch on Lu Jingming.

254
00:12:59,410 --> 00:13:00,820
- Go!
- Yes.

255
00:13:06,050 --> 00:13:07,220
How's it going on your side?

256
00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:08,650
- Young Master, My Lady.
- Yes.

257
00:13:09,810 --> 00:13:10,550
Young Master,

258
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:11,990
the arrow loading is more controlled,

259
00:13:12,050 --> 00:13:13,620
but the accuracy is still not good.

260
00:13:14,530 --> 00:13:15,460
Then you two

261
00:13:15,460 --> 00:13:17,220
can go find more materials

262
00:13:17,220 --> 00:13:18,890
that can be used for the bowstring.

263
00:13:18,890 --> 00:13:19,740
Go ahead.

264
00:13:19,740 --> 00:13:20,580
- Yes.
- Yes.

265
00:13:22,410 --> 00:13:23,250
Yunyi.

266
00:13:25,050 --> 00:13:25,890
I'll take the arrows.

267
00:13:26,430 --> 00:13:29,160
♪Stealing a bit of the starry sky,
making the encounter romantic♪

268
00:13:29,170 --> 00:13:30,170
Here, try it.

269
00:13:30,760 --> 00:13:34,220
♪The lights fade; the story isn't over♪

270
00:13:34,550 --> 00:13:37,770
♪Let's continue our fate♪

271
00:13:40,890 --> 00:13:41,730
You try it.

272
00:13:42,220 --> 00:13:43,440
But I don't know how to shoot.

273
00:13:44,570 --> 00:13:46,100
It's okay. Just try.

274
00:13:46,100 --> 00:13:47,580
I can teach you to shoot.

275
00:13:48,290 --> 00:13:51,680
♪Living all the joys, sorrows,
partings, and meetings♪

276
00:13:51,990 --> 00:13:55,180
♪Let's watch slowly♪

277
00:13:56,930 --> 00:13:57,980
Is it like this?

278
00:14:00,100 --> 00:14:00,940
Hold it here.

279
00:14:00,940 --> 00:14:04,940
♪Alas, this fate is full of misfortune♪

280
00:14:05,710 --> 00:14:08,330
♪But I refuse to accept♪

281
00:14:08,330 --> 00:14:13,430
♪That regret is
the only natural outcome♪

282
00:14:13,550 --> 00:14:18,310
♪So, I cross mountains and rivers♪

283
00:14:18,780 --> 00:14:22,650
♪Just to keep you by my side♪

284
00:14:25,290 --> 00:14:26,130
This time,

285
00:14:26,150 --> 00:14:27,860
it feels like honey
doesn't work very well.

