580
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:32,540
I must reward you properly.

581
00:28:35,340 --> 00:28:36,180
Father,

582
00:28:36,860 --> 00:28:37,700
I have

583
00:28:38,180 --> 00:28:39,460
a request.

584
00:28:40,500 --> 00:28:41,340
Tell me.

585
00:28:42,180 --> 00:28:43,380
I want the Lei Pill.

586
00:28:43,380 --> 00:28:44,580
You also want the Lei Pill?

587
00:28:45,220 --> 00:28:46,980
- Yes.
- Both you and your wife

588
00:28:46,980 --> 00:28:48,460
are asking for the Lei Pill from me.

589
00:28:48,820 --> 00:28:50,300
What's it for?

590
00:28:50,610 --> 00:28:51,450
My Lord,

591
00:28:51,460 --> 00:28:52,640
why ask so many questions?

592
00:28:52,680 --> 00:28:54,380
This time, Jingming
has done great service.

593
00:28:54,380 --> 00:28:55,700
He's contributed to the nation.

594
00:28:56,380 --> 00:28:57,820
This military demonstration

595
00:28:57,820 --> 00:28:59,620
has prevented many wars.

596
00:28:59,900 --> 00:29:01,420
All he's asking for is a pill.

597
00:29:03,620 --> 00:29:04,460
Father,

598
00:29:04,660 --> 00:29:05,860
Mother is right.

599
00:29:06,770 --> 00:29:08,410
Jingming is righteous,

600
00:29:08,630 --> 00:29:10,300
and Jiangli can save lives.

601
00:29:10,780 --> 00:29:12,700
They must be using the pill for good.

602
00:29:14,340 --> 00:29:16,220
Jingming has helped me resolve

603
00:29:16,220 --> 00:29:17,820
an urgent crisis in Dongzhou.

604
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:20,380
It's stabilized the national affairs.

605
00:29:21,180 --> 00:29:22,260
When the nation is stable,

606
00:29:22,500 --> 00:29:24,440
it can prosper,
and the people can live in peace.

607
00:29:24,580 --> 00:29:25,540
You can have

608
00:29:26,010 --> 00:29:26,870
the Lei Pill.

609
00:29:30,300 --> 00:29:31,140
Thank you, Father.

610
00:29:32,700 --> 00:29:33,740
There's one more thing.

611
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:37,220
Lately, Jingming has improved a lot.

612
00:29:37,660 --> 00:29:39,060
It's time for you to share

613
00:29:39,060 --> 00:29:40,100
my burdens.

614
00:29:40,900 --> 00:29:43,590
The position of Commander
of the Qilin Guards

615
00:29:43,590 --> 00:29:44,710
has been vacant for a while.

616
00:29:44,940 --> 00:29:46,020
From today onwards,

617
00:29:46,340 --> 00:29:47,540
it will be your responsibility.

618
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:52,380
Thank your father now.

619
00:29:54,900 --> 00:29:56,100
Thank you, Father.

620
00:30:00,940 --> 00:30:02,020
Congratulations, Jingming.

621
00:30:02,650 --> 00:30:04,160
In the future, if you have

622
00:30:04,160 --> 00:30:05,720
any doubts regarding military matters,

623
00:30:06,180 --> 00:30:07,660
feel free to consult me.

624
00:30:08,300 --> 00:30:09,780
The door to the Golden Guards

625
00:30:10,420 --> 00:30:12,020
will always be open to you.

626
00:30:13,100 --> 00:30:13,940
Thank you, Jingxiu.

627
00:30:19,540 --> 00:30:21,700
Now that you're the Commander
of the Qilin Guards,

628
00:30:21,700 --> 00:30:23,100
you'll have to make achievements

629
00:30:23,620 --> 00:30:25,570
to win everyone's respect.

630
00:30:28,620 --> 00:30:30,380
Today, the Astrology Bureau reported

631
00:30:30,700 --> 00:30:31,860
that an earthquake occurred

632
00:30:31,860 --> 00:30:32,900
in the southern suburbs,

633
00:30:33,300 --> 00:30:35,740
and the people are displaced
and suffering.

634
00:30:36,220 --> 00:30:37,140
Now,

635
00:30:37,290 --> 00:30:39,390
I command you to provide relief

636
00:30:39,690 --> 00:30:40,940
and comfort to the people there.

637
00:30:41,340 --> 00:30:42,220
Father, rest assured.

638
00:30:42,620 --> 00:30:44,430
I won't let you down.

639
00:30:45,750 --> 00:30:46,940
Congratulations, Jingming.

640
00:30:47,390 --> 00:30:49,630
You can be on equal footing with me now.

641
00:30:50,090 --> 00:30:52,140
I'm truly happy for you.

642
00:30:52,920 --> 00:30:54,220
Jingxiu, I'll need your guidance

643
00:30:54,220 --> 00:30:55,220
in the future.

644
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:57,280
Jingming,

645
00:30:57,740 --> 00:31:00,000
your crossbow was hidden quite deep.

646
00:31:01,100 --> 00:31:02,730
It wasn't hidden well enough,

647
00:31:03,020 --> 00:31:04,660
so the strings of 20 crossbows

648
00:31:04,660 --> 00:31:05,620
were cut,

649
00:31:06,100 --> 00:31:07,330
almost ruining the whole plan.

650
00:31:08,460 --> 00:31:09,820
How could this happen?

651
00:31:10,620 --> 00:31:12,460
Then, how did you find

652
00:31:12,460 --> 00:31:13,540
the silkworm silk again?

653
00:31:16,060 --> 00:31:16,900
Jingxiu,

654
00:31:17,820 --> 00:31:19,140
when did I ever tell you

655
00:31:19,700 --> 00:31:21,020
the strings of the crossbow

656
00:31:21,180 --> 00:31:22,340
were made of silkworm silk?

657
00:31:24,620 --> 00:31:26,890
I saw it today on the training grounds.

658
00:31:28,300 --> 00:31:29,780
Jingxiu, you truly have sharp eyes.

659
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:31,560
From such a distance,

660
00:31:31,720 --> 00:31:32,760
you can tell the material

661
00:31:32,820 --> 00:31:34,220
at a glance.

662
00:31:36,490 --> 00:31:37,840
The strings were all cut.

663
00:31:38,140 --> 00:31:38,980
Jingming,

664
00:31:39,380 --> 00:31:40,630
could it be

665
00:31:41,020 --> 00:31:42,100
an accident?

666
00:31:43,140 --> 00:31:44,420
I always prepare

667
00:31:45,460 --> 00:31:46,940
for the worst.

668
00:31:48,260 --> 00:31:49,540
In fact, I prepared

669
00:31:50,020 --> 00:31:51,340
these five crossbows in advance

670
00:31:51,340 --> 00:31:52,300
and stored them at home

671
00:31:53,810 --> 00:31:55,340
just to prevent such an accident.

672
00:31:59,620 --> 00:32:01,660
Jingming, you really plan ahead.

673
00:32:02,460 --> 00:32:03,620
Thank you for the compliment.

674
00:32:04,300 --> 00:32:05,820
I must go now to lead the Qilin Guards

675
00:32:05,820 --> 00:32:07,020
and complete Father's task.

676
00:32:07,460 --> 00:32:08,580
Goodbye.

677
00:32:09,700 --> 00:32:10,660
Go ahead, Jingming.

678
00:32:14,140 --> 00:32:15,660
The useless fools at home

679
00:32:16,380 --> 00:32:17,900
can't get anything done.

680
00:32:20,540 --> 00:32:21,380
Lord Zhou.

681
00:32:21,860 --> 00:32:22,860
Lord Zhou, please wait.

682
00:32:24,860 --> 00:32:25,780
Master Jingxiu,

683
00:32:25,780 --> 00:32:27,300
do you have some advice for me?

684
00:32:27,580 --> 00:32:28,420
I wouldn't dare.

685
00:32:28,860 --> 00:32:30,380
Lord Zhou, you are the first disciple

686
00:32:30,380 --> 00:32:31,560
of the Wind Pavilion's chief.

687
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:32,940
By observing the stars at night,

688
00:32:32,940 --> 00:32:34,660
you can see
the major events of the world.

689
00:32:34,780 --> 00:32:36,740
What could I possibly advise you on?

690
00:32:37,900 --> 00:32:38,900
However,

691
00:32:39,300 --> 00:32:41,460
as the Prefect's eldest lineal son,

692
00:32:41,980 --> 00:32:44,140
I'm quite concerned about the earthquake

693
00:32:44,860 --> 00:32:46,020
so I'd like to ask

694
00:32:46,490 --> 00:32:47,460
if you have any method

695
00:32:47,460 --> 00:32:49,780
to help the Prefect resolve
the immediate crisis.

696
00:32:51,980 --> 00:32:52,820
Well.

697
00:32:54,820 --> 00:32:55,660
Lord Zhou,

698
00:32:56,060 --> 00:32:58,220
why don't you come to my home
to discuss it in detail?

699
00:32:58,420 --> 00:33:00,340
I happen to acquire a piece

700
00:33:00,340 --> 00:33:01,580
of fine Hetian jade.

701
00:33:01,980 --> 00:33:02,820
Why don't we

702
00:33:03,100 --> 00:33:04,140
appreciate it together?

703
00:33:05,140 --> 00:33:05,980
Alright.

704
00:33:06,180 --> 00:33:07,020
I'll take the liberty

705
00:33:07,540 --> 00:33:09,180
to accept your invitation.

706
00:33:10,020 --> 00:33:10,860
Let's go.

707
00:33:23,060 --> 00:33:23,900
Jiangli.

708
00:33:29,580 --> 00:33:30,420
What's wrong?

709
00:33:31,020 --> 00:33:31,860
Take this.

710
00:33:32,380 --> 00:33:33,220
Take a look.

711
00:33:33,460 --> 00:33:34,300
What is this?

712
00:33:34,300 --> 00:33:35,140
Open it.

713
00:33:39,300 --> 00:33:40,140
The Lei Pill!

714
00:33:40,700 --> 00:33:41,660
This is the Lei Pill!

715
00:33:43,020 --> 00:33:43,860
That's great!

716
00:33:44,140 --> 00:33:44,980
With the Lei Pill,

717
00:33:45,300 --> 00:33:46,940
I can cure Yanyan.

718
00:33:55,420 --> 00:33:56,540
I'll go prepare the medicine.

719
00:34:01,740 --> 00:34:02,700
Thank you so much.

720
00:34:04,140 --> 00:34:05,500
It's what I should do.

721
00:34:14,820 --> 00:34:15,700
Yanyan.

722
00:34:15,700 --> 00:34:18,180
Mr. Cute, you've made up with Mother?

723
00:34:18,700 --> 00:34:20,020
Yes.

724
00:34:23,900 --> 00:34:25,700
Guess which hand I have something in.

725
00:34:29,140 --> 00:34:30,800
You can try your best
to take it from me.

726
00:34:30,940 --> 00:34:31,980
If you manage to take it,

727
00:34:32,140 --> 00:34:33,420
it'll be yours.

728
00:34:36,100 --> 00:34:38,180
Yanyan, you're so strong.

729
00:34:40,300 --> 00:34:41,220
What is it?

730
00:34:44,380 --> 00:34:45,220
Yanyan.

731
00:34:46,940 --> 00:34:47,780
Come on.

732
00:34:50,220 --> 00:34:51,420
Here, drink your medicine.

733
00:34:55,940 --> 00:34:57,020
Mother,

734
00:34:57,340 --> 00:34:58,980
what kind of medicine is this?

735
00:34:58,980 --> 00:35:00,260
It's so bitter.

736
00:35:00,580 --> 00:35:01,420
Yanyan,

737
00:35:01,580 --> 00:35:03,060
this is a very special medicine.

738
00:35:03,420 --> 00:35:04,630
After drinking it,

739
00:35:04,900 --> 00:35:06,700
your illness will never flare up again.

740
00:35:07,140 --> 00:35:07,980
Alright.

741
00:35:12,380 --> 00:35:14,140
Drink slowly so you don't choke.

742
00:35:20,180 --> 00:35:21,860
- Is it bitter?
- Yes.

743
00:35:23,380 --> 00:35:24,220
Here.

744
00:35:27,020 --> 00:35:27,860
Yanyan,

745
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:30,760
after you drink this special medicine,

746
00:35:30,860 --> 00:35:33,180
your body will become really strong.

747
00:35:33,420 --> 00:35:34,980
You can play cuju with me,

748
00:35:35,140 --> 00:35:36,500
and we can even shoot arrows.

749
00:35:37,060 --> 00:35:37,900
Would you like that?

750
00:35:38,060 --> 00:35:38,900
Sure.

751
00:35:39,260 --> 00:35:40,100
Good boy.

752
00:35:54,740 --> 00:35:56,100
Mother, Mr. Cute,

753
00:35:56,100 --> 00:35:57,420
come and look!

754
00:36:00,490 --> 00:36:03,330
♪The sound of the flute lingers,
making the night more tender♪

755
00:36:03,340 --> 00:36:04,280
What are we looking at?

756
00:36:04,980 --> 00:36:07,260
They seem like a family.

757
00:36:09,030 --> 00:36:12,560
♪The lights fade; the story isn't over♪

758
00:36:12,830 --> 00:36:16,050
♪Let's continue our fate♪

759
00:36:18,030 --> 00:36:21,730
♪Red candles glow, the wine flows free,
warming the long night♪

760
00:36:22,050 --> 00:36:25,970
♪Now I dare cross all lands and tides♪

761
00:36:26,520 --> 00:36:30,060
♪Living all the joys, sorrows,
partings, and meetings♪

762
00:36:30,280 --> 00:36:33,560
♪Let's watch slowly♪

763
00:36:40,620 --> 00:36:41,460
Yulan.

764
00:36:45,940 --> 00:36:47,240
Write a letter to Senior Brother.

765
00:36:47,530 --> 00:36:48,590
We must return

766
00:36:48,980 --> 00:36:50,100
to the Wind Pavilion asap.

767
00:36:50,420 --> 00:36:51,580
Yes, Jiangli.

768
00:36:56,340 --> 00:36:57,780
That potted bush lily has withered.

769
00:36:58,980 --> 00:37:00,060
Throw it away.

770
00:37:01,580 --> 00:37:02,420
Yes.

771
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:02,700
Are you going out?

772
00:38:05,940 --> 00:38:07,100
We are leaving.

773
00:38:08,380 --> 00:38:09,220
Leaving?

774
00:38:11,820 --> 00:38:13,060
I've got the Lei Pill,

775
00:38:14,420 --> 00:38:16,060
and you've got the Qilin Guards.

776
00:38:17,630 --> 00:38:18,960
With your wisdom,

777
00:38:20,250 --> 00:38:21,460
becoming the Young Prefect

778
00:38:22,020 --> 00:38:23,080
is only a matter of time.

779
00:38:24,100 --> 00:38:25,780
There's nothing more
I can help you with.

780
00:38:33,420 --> 00:38:34,460
Where are you going?

781
00:38:35,860 --> 00:38:37,300
To the place I came from.

782
00:38:55,660 --> 00:38:56,500
Don't worry.

783
00:38:57,860 --> 00:38:58,740
I will honor

784
00:38:59,180 --> 00:39:00,500
our previous agreement.

785
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:11,820
Yanyan,

786
00:39:13,260 --> 00:39:14,180
this is for you.

787
00:39:15,500 --> 00:39:16,340
Thank you.

788
00:39:20,900 --> 00:39:21,860
Actually,

789
00:39:23,180 --> 00:39:24,820
Yanyan hasn't fully recovered.

790
00:39:25,500 --> 00:39:26,980
You can stay here a little longer.

791
00:39:27,460 --> 00:39:28,620
After all,

792
00:39:28,780 --> 00:39:30,220
he can receive better care here.

793
00:39:31,900 --> 00:39:33,020
We've already gotten

794
00:39:33,020 --> 00:39:34,500
what we wanted.

795
00:39:35,900 --> 00:39:36,860
It's time for us

796
00:39:39,540 --> 00:39:40,900
to part ways.

797
00:39:47,740 --> 00:39:48,580
Yes.

798
00:39:50,260 --> 00:39:51,140
When will you leave?

799
00:39:53,100 --> 00:39:54,040
The day after tomorrow.

800
00:40:40,718 --> 00:40:44,478
♪The sound of the flute lingers,
making the night more tender♪

801
00:40:44,848 --> 00:40:48,548
♪Stealing a bit of the starry sky,
making the encounter romantic♪

802
00:40:49,148 --> 00:40:52,698
♪The lights fade; the story isn't over♪

803
00:40:52,948 --> 00:40:56,468
♪Let's continue our fate♪

804
00:40:58,088 --> 00:41:02,058
♪A cup of wine
to honor courage and love's trials♪

805
00:41:02,268 --> 00:41:06,178
♪For you, I'd dare to travel,
however long the journey is♪

806
00:41:06,558 --> 00:41:10,218
♪The world's many twists
end in separation♪

807
00:41:10,398 --> 00:41:14,078
♪I can't bear to watch♪

808
00:41:14,778 --> 00:41:19,228
♪This mortal world is full of hardships♪

809
00:41:19,228 --> 00:41:23,568
♪Alas, this fate is full of misfortune♪

810
00:41:24,068 --> 00:41:26,688
♪But I refuse to accept♪

811
00:41:26,688 --> 00:41:31,548
♪That regret is
the only natural outcome♪

